<p>Any one of the passengers/the passenger booked on I-ticket, undertaking journey in AC-3 tier, AC-2 tier, 1st AC, AC Chair Car and Executive Classes, will also have to carry any one of the ten prescribed proofs of identity in original) during the journey and produce the same failing which all the passengers booked on that ticket will be treated as without ticket and charged accordingly w.e.f. 15-02-2012</p>
 
